quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,Na u lemoha ea koenehang
  53,34,A fana hanyenyane le hona ho tiisa pelo
  53,35,Eng! Na o na le tsebo ka Liphiri hoo a li bonang
  53,36,"Che, ha a na tsebo ka litaba tse ka har’a mangolo a Moshe –"
  53,37,"Le Abrahama ea ileng a phethahatsa litaelo: –"
  53,38,Tsa hore ha ho motho ea ka jarang mojaro oa motho e mong
  53,39,"Hore ha ho motho ofe, kapa ofe ea tla amohela seo a sa se sebeletsang"
  53,40,Hore ts’ebetso ea hae e tla hlahela pooaneng
  53,41,"Joale, o tla lefshoa ho latela ts’ebetso eo ka tefo e feletseng"
  53,42,Hore ho Mong`a hau ke katlehong ea qetelo
  53,43,Hore ke Eena ea faneng ka Nyakallo le Lillo
  53,44,Hore ke Eena ea fanang ka Lefu le Bophelo
  53,45,"Hore ke Eena ea hlotseng lintho ka bobeli, – tse tona le tse ts’ehali"
  53,46,Ho tsoa lerotholing le tsoileng
  53,47,Hore ke Eena ea ts’episitseng Tsoho bophelong bo-tlang
  53,48,Hore ke Eena ea fanang ka Borui le Khotsofalo
  53,49,Hore ke Eena Mong`a Sirius (Naleli e Kholo)
  53,50,Le hore ke Eena ea ripitlileng morabe oa mathomo oa Ba – A’d
  53,51,"Le Ba-Thamude, ha ho ope ea ileng a phonyoha"
  53,52,"Le batho ba habo Nooe pele ho bona, hobane e ne e le bahanyapetsi, batloli ba meeli"
  53,53,U bile A ripitla le Metse (Ea Sodoma le Gomorah)
  53,54,Hore e koaelehe
  53,55,"Joale, ke mahlohonolo afe a Mong`a hau ao uena motho o ka a phehisang khang"
  53,56,Enoa ke molemosi oa ba lemosi ba ileng ba tla khale-khale
  53,57,Kahlolo e ea e ntse e atamela haufi
  53,58,"Ha ho mang, haese Allah feela Ea ka e utullang"
  53,59,Na le makalitsoe ke boemo boo ba litaba
  53,60,"Ebile le ea nyakalla, le fapana le ho lla, –"
  53,61,Le qhala nako ea lona ka mafeela
  53,62,Empa le ithapalatsa kapel’a Allah le Mo sebeletse ka lerato